# 🌬️ Breath Easy - Low-Cost Ventilator  

[![Website](https://img.shields.io/badge/Visit-Website-blue?style=for-the-badge)](https://breath-easy.netlify.app/)  
[![GitHub License](https://img.shields.io/github/license/your-username/your-repo?style=for-the-badge)](LICENSE)  

## 🏥 About the Project  
**Breath Easy** is an affordable ventilator designed to provide life-saving respiratory support in resource-limited settings. The project integrates real-time monitoring, user-friendly control, and IoT-based alert systems to ensure accessibility and efficiency.

## 🌐 Live Website  
🔗 **[Visit Our Website](https://breath-easy.netlify.app/)**  


